



			Navigation










		o  cursor keys

		o  home keys

			o h  -  1 space back		***
			o j  -  1 space down		***
			o k  -  1 space up		***
			o l  -  1 space forward		***

		o  screen keys

			o H -  Home or 1st Line
			o M -  Middle Line
			o L -  Last Line

		o control keys

			o CTRL-B - back a screen
			o CTRL-F - forward a screen
			o CTRL-U - Up half a screen
			o CTRL-D - Down half a screen


		*** a numeric count can be added before the command.

